Package ie.gmit.sw.sprites.entities

Class Human

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.sw.sprites.entities.Entity
      • ie.gmit.sw.sprites.entities.Human
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Player

    public abstract class Human
extends Entity
    Returns position and size of a Human to the screen. Checks for collision using moving position and bounds. Human is no longer able to cross water tiles.
    Author:
    Kamila Michel
